{"tid":909132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「陳健康」避席英文選舉論壇","createTime":"2018-11-20T06:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T07:30:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9992424ca5d5593d6112c7d3741c2e35717fe2","tid":909132,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181120/20550330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F20550330&d=GLHxB1Bl6fk81vWTn2Ta6zOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=bba4c93a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F20550330&h=67a623f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181120/20550330</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月20日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：「陳健康」避席英文選舉論壇 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181120/large/chan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181120%2Flarge%2Fchan.jpg&h=70e6a621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n九西補選進入大直路，候選人都埋牙肉搏，而喺全面缺席地區團體舉辦嘅論壇之時，獲建制派支持出選嘅陳凱欣（圖）都好畀面，出席晒各大電子傳媒舉辦嘅論壇，可能話晒以前都係傳媒人，都會多一份親切感。但，咪住，去到今日，竟然首度缺席電子傳媒舉辦嘅選舉論壇，因乜事佢唔喺呢個節目亮相？睇返吖，原來係港台英文台第三台Backchat嘅特備節目，同之前嘅論壇唯一之別，除咗講英文，好似冇。<br />\n<br />\n根據港台發出嘅採訪通知，今早8點半至9點半嘅節目，除咗陳凱欣，其餘4名候選人包括「劏房阿哥」伍廸希、工黨李卓人、前民協馮檢基以及曾麗文，個個都會現身，親自以英文辯出火花。港台喺採訪通知冇講明，點解陳凱欣唔嚟；陳凱欣助選團回應八方話，因為陳凱欣行程緊密及已安排競選活動，所以未能出席有關論壇喎。  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：特首辦殘體字塗鴉　85歲老翁被捕 (李八方)"},{"pid":"9a803e0d5eba74fcebc8a8e4c815997d943006b6","tid":909132,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"建制派除咗葉劉淑儀曾鈺成嗰一輩之外其他都收得皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea776d3d0c300bdb229987ea0f20afe1df351dd","tid":909132,"uid":62983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"現任議員英文最好係咪毛姨姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8250493b4f17dbedf3dd660816333a6fbd19fa4f","tid":909132,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"一講英文就梗係潛水啦<br />\n學歷買返嚟咋"},{"pid":"d455ae94ca71a32f2b6cd184fbd28f8689ffd60c","tid":909132,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"諗起黃成智 一聽話講英文就不了"},{"pid":"e3fc26dd079fff9da3f3f1da6b71b1121f403506","tid":909132,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"廢柴係咪柒到英文稿都唔識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fdca88ccee2f7416e715ea6f306f0830115612d","tid":909132,"uid":91783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"英文聽眾根本唔係建制派目標"},{"pid":"e1c2ff3db31b275c598514b9f538ee0cfb00ffc8","tid":909132,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:30:13.000Z","msg":"以為廿年前嗰個"}]}